rows.label: bf06230120_0010
rows.name:
Oh, my- This is the very picture of the
ancient civilizations I've read about!

rows.label: bf06230120_0030
rows.name: You know the old land of Iira?

rows.label: bf06230120_0040
rows.name:
They had a proud and noble civilization,
rivaled only by Judicium at the time.

rows.label: bf06230120_0050
rows.name:
But whereas Judicium were the masters of
biological arts...

rows.label: bf06230120_0060
rows.name: Iirans knew all there was to know about engineering.

rows.label: bf06230120_0070
rows.name:
The proud blood of Iira runs in
the veins of us Luxurian.

rows.label: bf06230120_0080
rows.name:
As there are people to pass it on to,
civilization will endure.

rows.label: bf06230120_0090
rows.name: Knowledge is inherited, much like life itself.

rows.label: bf06230120_0100
rows.name: Nice quote! You should write that down.
